title: Magic Boobs: Multitouch Tits! v1.01
description:
An official successor of Magic Butt - Interactive Ass!
A new live wallpaper with many improvements!
See for yourself - watch the video!

Now featuring a sexy girl with boobies that you can stretch, squeeze, pinch, shake and more!

Fun every time you unlock your phone or tablet - it's a live wallpaper that appears as your launcher's background!

No ads of any kind.

Caution:
During the testing phase we found out it can make girls jealous!

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Supports phones and tablets with all Android versions since Android 2.1. Tested also on Android 4.0 (ICS).
Supports multitouch up to 10 fingers (and more if your device allows).
Supports 3-axis accelerometer for shaking in all directions!
Fully customizable physics simulation parameters.
Doesn't request any unsafe or not needed permissions!

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Improvements since Magic Butt v1.02:

- Performance optimizations that allowed 16 times greater morphing accuracy!
- Improved physics simulation.
- Removed strict licensing policy - now you should never get any license errors.
- Interactive hanging necklace.
- Higher quality graphics with no visible boundaries in color gradients.
- Well, there are tits now!

What's in this version:

- Improved skin and necklace physics.
- Two new physical parameters of the skin available to adjust in the settings screen.
- Many minor improvements.
